  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the utility of a portable motion sensor-based system
      designed to monitor essential tremor (ET) to better prescribe therapy to minimize symptoms
      and expand care for ET patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
